situation: I will be losing my job in January.  I am very worried about finding a new one.

final_result.label: normal
final_result.response: It's completely understandable to want both stability and a fulfilling role. Maybe you could explore job options that align closely with your skills and interests while also considering temporary positions that can provide some stability in the meantime. Would you like to brainstorm some potential job roles together or look into ways to enhance your skill set?
